{"tid":536740,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加轟山狗為錢入「魔」","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T07:01:23.000Z","uid":57035,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5a0c074f463c1e3993b872ef561e56c0d4b242","tid":536740,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2sqDBBqJzP5ZBWXjfw5LScVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=71fe7d40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加炮轟即將加盟曼聯的阿歷斯山齊士，只為錢而轉會。<br />\n29歲的阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）從阿仙奴改投曼聯一事，相信在日內就會落實，有傳他將獲得40萬鎊周薪的4年半合約，而且有1500萬鎊的簽約費，成為全英超最高薪球員。 雲加（Arsene Wenger）表示：「我不明白為甚麼有球員想離開阿仙奴，但從事了30年轉會，你多少學懂一點人性。作為職業球員，這或許是他最後一份頂級合約了。之後，我跟球會都要接受放他走，再去分析事情的好處及壞處。」 山神加盟曼聯，有指是跟紅魔攻中米希達利恩直接作交換，雲加也暗示說：「我們有強大的陣容，不是只依靠一名球員，而且可不要忘記，要是山齊士離開，也會有一名具質素的球員來投。再者，我們在轉會市場也會嘗試增兵。」"},{"pid":"bb7cb0c6d5a95be0ba56093f2878c9a76f613144","tid":536740,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>。再者，我們在轉會市場也會<span style=\"color: red;\">嘗試</span>增兵。」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"53780ea902fba46528a2c68e550381dd51348567","tid":536740,"uid":4308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以就減鳩韋舒亞人工<br />\n唔續約就係為錢"},{"pid":"07079576af1bde24f1f13aaaa05ad5c1f58b23a9","tid":536740,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"雲格為錢唔撚走"},{"pid":"040f33e1b7645a8fa918c413c55dcd4fe1352f31","tid":536740,"uid":76681,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"aa5a0c074f463c1e3993b872ef561e56c0d4b242","tid":536740,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2sqDBBqJzP5ZBWXjfw5LScVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7